* Changes from FlickrDownload 0.3 to 0.4
  - Rewritten in Java instead of C#.
  - New XML file format contains more Flickr metadata.
  - Added support for downloading collection information and videos.
  - Added page with statistics about your Flickr account.
  - The statistics page shows duplicate photos on your account.

* Changes from FlickrDownload 0.2 to 0.3
  - Fixed bug if a relative path was specified on the command line.
  - The footer message is now stored in the toplevel XML configuration file
    along with the Flickr username.
  - The square thumbnails are now retrieved from Flickr.
